{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_看进山路",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·看进山路 + 夜路喊名（心理抗性）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_xungou_main",
              "state": "s09_songhuo",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "不看了。那条路看人的时候，比人看它的时候多。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "棚子后头，那条进山的路扎进雾里，看不到第十步。两边的树静得不对——鸟都不落。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（过了岭，就是神仙顶……李天狗当年，走的就是这条道？）",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "盯着盯着，一股寒气顺着脊梁骨往上爬。他打了个寒颤，啐了一口，掉头就走——",
      "next": "n_night"
    },
    "n_night": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "songhuo_gazed"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldToBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 900
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playScriptedDialogue",
          "params": {
            "lines": [
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "下山一半，天彻底黑透。林子里的虫鸣，一声一声稀下去——然后，没了。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_hold"
    },
    "n_hold": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldFromBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 600
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "forest_name_call"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "下到山脚，回头望——林子黑沉沉的，什么都没有。脚帮那句闲话，他算是亲身验过了：山里喊名，千万别应。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（它凑近看了俺一眼……认不准俺是个什么。——为什么认不准？）",
      "next": "n_sig"
    },
    "n_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "songhuo_returned"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playScriptedDialogue",
          "params": {
            "lines": [
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "回到城里，他给自己灌了二两烧酒。酒入喉是热的，后脖颈还是凉的。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}